summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Forty-fifth Avenue Southwest from West Edmonds Street to West Hanford Street, et al. in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 24843, creating Local Improvement District No. 2383 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
